OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,FThe Troubles, Covid and a rising
OL,7,Fmenace of drugs have blighted
OL,8,FBelfast's nightlife.
OL,10,FNew research by the Consumer Council,
OL,11,Freported by , also reveals a majority
OL,12,Fof people are concerned for their
OL,13,Fsafety when hitting the town.
OL,15,FAnd with current licensing laws and a
OL,16,Flack of transport options, business
OL,17,Ffaces an uphill battle to attract
OL,18,Fpeople.
