OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,FBut the pubs, clubs, restaurants and
OL,7,Fothers businesses which light up the
OL,8,Fnight in the city have come together
OL,9,Fand are working on how to make Belfast
OL,10,Fone of the best destinations for a
OL,11,Fnight out.
OL,13,FUTV current affairs programme Up Close
OL,14,Fspoke to key figures in the
OL,15,Fhospitality and transport industries,
OL,16,Fcouncillors, consumer and business
OL,17,Fgroups and campaigners to try to
OL,18,Funpick the issues having an impact on
OL,19,FBelfast's burgeoning nightlife scene,
OL,20,Fand what their thoughts are on
OL,21,Fsolutions.
