OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,FDamien Corr, of Destination CQ, one of
OL,7,Fthe city's business improvement
OL,8,Fdistricts (BID) which represents
OL,9,Faround 700 organisations, said its
OL,10,Fresearch found people spent #150 on
OL,11,Faverage when out in the town over a
OL,12,Flong weekend.
OL,14,F"Even if they are only spending a
OL,15,Ffraction of that, you can see the
OL,16,Fvalue," he said.
OL,18,FThree of the city's BIDs are working
OL,19,Fon employing their own nighttime
OL,20,Fchampion to work to reform the city.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/9
