OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,F"We have decided to put our money
OL,7,Fwhere our mouth is," Damien added.
OL,9,F"We have a modest amount of money... I
OL,10,Fdunno if we will call it a czar...
OL,11,FMaybe a nighttime champion. But that
OL,12,Fneeds to happen soon."
OL,14,FPublican Willie Jack has been in the
OL,15,Ftrade for five decades. He said a "big
OL,16,Fpersonality" was needed.
OL,18,F"We need someone that can pull all the
OL,19,Fservices together... make the city
OL,20,Fsafe, that's the biggest thing they
OL,21,Fcan do. We need a night time czar."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/9
