OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,FBoyd Sleator, of Free the Night, a
OL,7,Fcampaign group lobbying for better
OL,8,Fnightlife, said there was a lot to do
OL,9,Fto open the city up to more people and
OL,10,Fany night time champion had to be
OL,11,Findependent.
OL,13,FThat includes bringing in new "young
OL,14,Fcurators" into the city, relaxing
OL,15,Flicensing laws, reforming transport.
OL,17,F"And really consider the benefits of
OL,18,Fculture in a post conflict society in
OL,19,Fa shared city like Belfast," he said,
OL,20,F"And it is very do-able".
