OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,F"We do have the building blocks and we
OL,7,Fhave the people for it, but it comes
OL,8,Fdown to the infrastructure," he said.
OL,9,FThe lack of taxis to get home was
OL,10,Ffound to be an issue for people
OL,11,Fconsidering heading out into Belfast.
OL,12,FTranslink said it wanted to expand its
OL,13,Fseasonal nighttime offerings to all
OL,14,Fyear. but needed the investment.JSDLP
OL,15,Fcouncillor Seamus de Faoite estimates
OL,16,Faround #150,000 a year is needed to
OL,17,Frun night time services.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/9
