OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,F"When you look at the multiplier
OL,7,Feffect of what that does to the
OL,8,Fnighttime economy- it is huge. We want
OL,9,Fthis to happen."
OL,11,FResponding, Infrastructure Minister
OL,12,FJohn O'Dowd said scheduling was a
OL,13,Fmatter for the public transport
OL,14,Foperator.
OL,16,FTaxi driver numbers have also had an
OL,17,Feffect. Before Covid there were around
OL,18,F1,400 drivers. That number is now
OL,19,Fcloser to 1,000 and it is half the
OL,20,Fnumber there were a decade ago.
