OL,3,CHow to have a good night out in
OL,4,CBelfast?
OL,6,FWilliam McCausland says the test for
OL,7,Fdrivers sets a high bar and it is an
OL,8,Fobstacle for many. Around two thirds
OL,9,Ffail it.
OL,11,FMinister John O'Dowd said the 80% pass
OL,12,Fmark for the test was already the
OL,13,Flowest of all vocational theory tests
OL,14,F- and to reduce it would "undermine
OL,15,Fthe purpose of the test".
